OL,3,CWoman begged armed hotel intruder
OL,4,C'don't hurt me, I have children'
OL,6,FA "terrified" woman begged an armed
OL,7,Fintruder "please don't hurt me, I have
OL,8,Fchildren" when he barged into her
OL,9,Fhotel room.
OL,11,FChristopher Prior, 39, stole a knife
OL,12,Ffrom an Italian restaurant before
OL,13,Fforcing his way into the woman's room
OL,14,Fat the Double Tree by Hilton Hotel in
OL,15,FHull, a court heard.
OL,17,FThe victim thought she was going to be
OL,18,Fkilled during the ordeal, Hull Crown
OL,19,FCourt was told.
