OL,3,CWoman begged armed hotel intruder
OL,4,C'don't hurt me, I have children'
OL,6,FProsecutor Michael Masson said Prior
OL,7,Ftook a knife from a restaurant on
OL,8,FPrinces Avenue through an open back
OL,9,Fdoor.
OL,11,FHe then got into an elderly couple's
OL,12,Fhome through a patio door and then
OL,13,Fwent to a Travelodge hotel, where he
OL,14,Ffailed to get through the guest access
OL,15,Fdoor.
OL,17,FAt 7pm, he went to the DoubleTree by
OL,18,FHilton Hotel in Ferensway and knocked
OL,19,Fon the door of a woman who was waiting
OL,20,Ffor a takeaway delivery.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
