OL,3,CWoman begged armed hotel intruder
OL,4,C'don't hurt me, I have children'
OL,6,FPrior admitted false imprisonment,
OL,7,Fburglary and possessing a knife.
OL,9,FJailing him for three years, Judge
OL,10,FTahir Khan KC told Prior: "It must
OL,11,Fhave been, for her, an excruciating
OL,12,Fperiod of time and then you did leave.
OL,13,FThe trauma she went through includes
OL,14,Fher being fearful for her life and
OL,15,Falso having flashbacks. This was an
OL,16,Foffence of false imprisonment of some
OL,17,Fgravity.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
